thread.title: Peter Aawen

author: Peter Aawen
title: Peter Aawen
text: Open Agent was extremely helpful in identifying Agents who had a proven track record of successful sales in our area & price range. They quickly identified what was important to us and focussed their recommendations on Agents who excelled in those areas & had a range of strategies to choose from in achieving our aim of selling and achieving a good price for our home. The Open Agent staff were always professional, polite, & helpful without being pushy or overly intrusive, making the task of searching for & identifying Agents a whole lot easier. Highly recommend their service.
